data.description: Very well maintained home with a great split floor plan. Beautiful wood laminate floors throughout. The spacious family room has large beautiful windows that offer tons of natural light. The kitchen has a very nice breakfast bar that overlooks the family room and dining area. Right off the kitchen is access to the nice covered patio that has a magnificent view of the pond. The large master suit has a nice tub with jets, separate shower, double vanities and a walk in closet. The two other bedrooms are on the opposite side of the house and share a full bath. Upstairs there is an unfinished expandable and accesses to the floored attic. This charming home is located near the casinos and Memphis. Do not miss out on all this house has to offer!!!
